Posts.Content: I went to the Doc Monday, Told her you know how I 've been complaining about my left breast area bothering me for months now? Well I think I feel something on that breast now (a knot or lump) so she feels, and then says to me, even though nothing showed up on the mammo it did show dense breast I do feel a mass so I want to get you a Biopsy next Tuesday I said o.k. So my question for you more experciensed what is my chances here? I'm really worried.
Posts.Title: Going for first Biopsy
